npc.stella.2: This is where you can create, delete or switch SkyBlock Profiles.
npc.stella.3: Enter /coop followed by the name of all the friends you want to invite!

npc.bea.0: Hello! Do you have a pet?

npc.george.2: If you have any pets which need a new home I'd be happy to buy them off you!

npc.blacksmith.welcome.2: Go into the Mine to collect Coal and return to learn how to reforge items!
npc.blacksmith.complete.1: Reforging item allows you to get the most out of your weapons, armor, and other items by applying stat modifiers to them!
npc.blacksmith.complete.2: To reforge an item, place an item in my inventory. Reforging costs Coins - the more prestigious items cost more to reforge!
npc.blacksmith.complete.3: However, this time I will reforge any item for the low price of 10 coal!
npc.marco.welcome.1: I'm a world-famous artist to be. Most people just call me "the new da Vinci."
npc.marco.welcome.2: Unfortunately, I ran out of dye this morning...
npc.marco.welcome.3: In my garden are some flowers. Could you pick 5 Dandelions and turn them into Rose Red Dye, then bring them back to me?
npc.marco.quest.0: Wow! That's the most beautiful red dye I have ever seen!
npc.marco.quest.2: You can select a spray by left-clicking your Spray Can!
npc.marco.quest.3: Right-click any wall on your private island to spray it. If you ever lose your Spray Can, you can craft another one using the recipe in your Recipe Book!
npc.marco.quest.4: Thank you so much for your help. You should visit me in my Canvas Room sometime! Step into the portal to the left over there!
npc.marco.complete.0: Before spraying on a wall, consider previewing it in the menu! Right-click on any spray of your choice and it'll magically appear in your hand.
npc.marco.complete.1: Don't forget to refill your spray can with dye! You can pick some of the flowers in my garden if you want to.
npc.marco.complete.2: You can select sprays by left-clicking with your Spray Can!
